videos.headline: Kessel: 'We have to just go to Pittsburgh and play our game'
videos.description: Penguins right winger Phil Kessel explains how the Penguins were able to stretch the series lead over the Sharks to 3-1 and what Pittsburgh needs to do to win one more game and capture the Stanley Cup.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Kessel: 'We have to just go to Pittsburgh and play our game') 2016/06/06 SC

videos.headline: Melrose: Penguins on top of their game
videos.description: Barry Melrose breaks down how well Pittsburgh is playing against San Jose in the Stanley Cup finals after winning Game 4 and now being a game away from winning the championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Melrose: Penguins on top of their game) 2016/06/06 SC
